computeST

public void computeST()
Invoked by ReflRouter when MST must be recomputed. It computes two vectors of tunnels (commands) that must be activated (toActivate) and deactivated (toDeactivate) in order to convert the current tree to the minimum spanning tree. A selected tunnel consist of link from A to B and from B to A i.e. both must be selected and the selection is made taking into account both links' quality.
